# Optional — FREE Google Sheet + Apps Script. Customer page posts without staff Settings.
# Build: copy to ".env", set URL, then npm run build. Upload "build" to your existing website.
#
# Customer link on your site = same URL with NO ?staff=1 (inquiry form only).
# Staff hub = same URL with ?staff=1 — bookmark internally only; never put on the public site.
# Public POSTs include customerConfirmation so Apps Script can MailApp.sendEmail to the customer.
#
# REACT_APP_GOOGLE_SHEETS_WEBHOOK_URL=https://script.google.com/macros/s/XXXX/exec
# REACT_APP_EMAIL_WEBHOOK_URL=
#
# GitHub Pages: add the SAME variable name as a repository Actions secret (Settings → Secrets
# and variables → Actions → New repository secret). No quotes. Redeploy after saving.
